Title: Juiskers II: The Sequel with No Prequel
Writer: Cody Maupin, Patrick Maupin, Rick Mushinski
Actors: Christine Condreay, Conrad Condreay, Nathan Walker Gray, Miles Johnson
Plot: After a frustrating experience with an uncooperative cable company, brothers Cody and Patrick Maupin decide to scrap their original idea, (A sketch show on local cable access TV) and make a sketch comedy movie.
